Our beauty salon equipment and hair salon chairs are designed and determined to showcase the uniqueness of each salon. For example, The Veronica hair salon chair exudes and reflects the elegant yet simple gal who appreciates the little things in life. Not to be confused with the one-of-a-kind Charlotte hair salon chair. This dame follows the latest trends and is not one to be played. Duke beauty salon chair on the other hand, enjoys his single barrel whiskey and is never caught without his alluring secret weapon that will snag any woman; high quality leather. While Duke hooks the girls, his wingman, the Draper hair salon chair, reels them in! His sleek and broad body is old-school and enjoys a hard Scotch on the rocks.We don't just have exquisite salon styling chairs, but we have a variety of types of hair salon chairs aimed to make salon life easier on clients, stylists, and receptionists alike! Our shampoo chairs are built with comfort in mind. Paired with one of our wall-mount shampoo bowls for salons, these various pairs of dynamic duos can make a shampoo experience even better! Your receptionist is the brains of a hair salon, so treat him or her to one of our high-quality salon reception chairs. With a comfortable chair, spending all day talking to clients will be just that much easier for them, leaving you at ease with your salon environment. Don't let your salon miss out on the wonderful array of hair salon chairs and salon equipment for sale at Standish.     All of our hair salon equipment has personality, as does all of the Standish hair salon furniture; which is why we are confident that our hair salon chairs tell their own stories. Browse our extensive selection of hair salon equipment for hair salon chairs that fit into your individual salon and unique story.Want to pair these hair salon chairs with one of Standish's salon styling stations? We've got plenty stylish salon styling stations to choose from, and one will be bound to blow you away. If you find one you like, you can always check out one of our hair salon furniture packages, that will pair up a chair, station, and mat that we know look great together, and you can order as many of that package as you might need! With our salon furniture packages, you also quality for an awesome package discount that you won't find anywhere else, or even quality for one of our Standish's beauty salon equipment monthly promotions! Check out our salon furniture packages page for details.  




 
