Want a shampoo bowl? We've got 7 wall-mount shampoo bowls that will spice up your salon, and are available in both black and white, with a variety of plastic and porcelain. Our salon shampoo bowl collection is outfitted beautifully, and shines like diamonds! And you can't just let your salon shampoo bowls hang out by themselves! Dont' have wall space? Check out the new line of Manchester Shampoo Cabinet Units. Available in black, chocolate, espresso, and cherry maple, this unique unit allows you the efficiency of a shampoo bowl, with the style and transportability of the line of London salon styling stations! Our salon shampoo chairs can be paired with any of our wall-mount shampoo bowls or shampoo cabinet units. Some of the features of the Standish shampoo chairs are: arm rests, raised foot rests, and fully-reclining capabilities. Check out the stylish and efficient group of Standish shampoo chairs today! Now, you're really in for a treat! Standish's line of shampoo backwash units are the best you'll find. Inspired by our line of hair salon styling chairs, our shampoo units are made with the seats of chairs such as the Charlotte hair salon chair, Veronica hair salon chair, and many more, but with a shampoo shuttle attached! This isn't your average shampoo unit. Each one of our chairs are customizable, from the color of the shampoo bowl--available in black or white--and the chair color, in black, brown, white, and for some--red! That's not even the best part! Our shampoo units are made to make your customers as comfortable as possible, so instead of reaching for the bowl, you can bring the shampoo bowl to them! The unique line of Standish shampoo units are tilt-bowls that, well, tilt the bowl to wherever your customer's head may be!  




 
