We have any style of salon equipment packages you can imagine to fit the theme and atmosphere of your salon! Some are inspired by our wonderful customers, such as the Envy, Loft Boutique, Wen Chic, and Hair Force. Others, we put together as inspiration when we first started Standish, which includes the Cortege on Canal, Barber Shop, Gentleman's Parlor, A Classic Affair, Modern Oasis, and Salon de Paris. From sophisticated to rugged and everything between, our salon furniture packages are high-fashion enough to attract the Stepford wife with a glass of merlot in her hand, and sturdy enough to support the Paul Bunyan-esque handyman. Yep, our salon furniture packages will fit just about anyones fantasy, with their prime combinations of salon stations and hair salon chairs. Browse our extensive selection of salon equipment packages for affordable beauty salon equipment for sale, and try to keep your mouth from dropping to the floor when you see our incomparable prices.When you're looking for the best beauty salon equipment packages, keep in mind that Standish has a great discount on high quality beauty salon equipment! !  




 
