Benefits and Features for this product







Mr. William Rufus Barber Chair Product Description  Review this item

Originally hailing from the foothills of the Great Smoky Mountains, the Mr. William Rufus Barber Chair is Rutherford's revered grandfather who's seen it all and has stories to boot. But don't call this barber chair old or a grandpa. He's a stylish, fedora-wearing young soul, who is always the life of the party. He's known around town as the hair salon chair with a handlebar mustache, but what people take note of is his reputation for quality. He's the kind of salon chair who believes in a hard day's work and can be seen with a glass of Guinness from time to time. As a barbershop owner, cultivating the culture and feel for your barber shop is key. Mr. William Rufus Barber Chair does just that.  He allows barbershops to stay classic while incorporating a notably modern, sleek look. Saddle up and take some time to get to know Mr. William Rufus Barber Chair. This barber chair will make any shop inviting to the ultimate mans man. 




Product Details
  Sleek black design with chrome finish Fully reclining barber chair 2 year warranty included Quality upholstery  Steel reinforced chair top U.S. quality control All equipment requires some assembly Seat width of 21" 35" H x 30" W x 30" D 












